Localization.Name: Calva Helmet
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Flight Helmet
Damage Reduction: 10%
Temp. Rating: -30 / 60 °C
Radiation Protection: 15200 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 81 REM/s

Get a clear view of everything around you with the Calva helmet from Quirinus Tech. The large face shield made from proprietary synthetic sapphire provides scratch resistance while remaining just as thin and light as typical materials.
